cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.DS

This paper focuses on reducing the memory consumption of embedding vectors in recommender systems, which is a common problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as they also deal with similar problems. Additionally, since the proposed method involves quantization, which is a common technique in computer vision, cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also a likely category. Finally, since the paper deals with large-scale data, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category.
